=head1 DESCRIPTION

Encapsulates settings for enabling C<QueryInsights> on an
C<ExecuteScheduledQueryRequest>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Mode => Str

Provides the following modes to enable C<ScheduledQueryInsights>:

=over

=item *

C<ENABLED_WITH_RATE_CONTROL> E<ndash> Enables C<ScheduledQueryInsights>
for the queries being processed. This mode also includes a rate control
mechanism, which limits the C<QueryInsights> feature to 1 query per
second (QPS).

=item *

C<DISABLED> E<ndash> Disables C<ScheduledQueryInsights>.

=back




